                            <comment id="16913146" author="mxm" created="Thu, 22 Aug 2019 08:50:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I believe this is caused by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-13367&quot; title=&quot;Make ClosureCleaner detect writeReplace serialization override&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-13367&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-13367&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and we have to wait for Flink 1.8.2.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16919079" author="sunjincheng121" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2019 01:04:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks report this issue and share your analysis&#160;and I agree with you this caused by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-13367&quot; title=&quot;Make ClosureCleaner detect writeReplace serialization override&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-13367&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-13367&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mxm&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mxm&quot;&gt;mxm&lt;/a&gt;&#160;!&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=markflyhigh&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;markflyhigh&quot;&gt;markflyhigh&lt;/a&gt;&#160;Already bring up the PROPOSAL for the Beam 2.16 release, and&#160;Beam 2.16 release branch cut is scheduled on Sep 11.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m not sure if I bringup the discuss of Flink-1.8.2 release today can catch up with Beam 2.16 release(Sep 11), but I think even if 2.16 can&apos;t merge this&#160;ticket we also need to push Flink-1.8.2 release as soon as possible, So that we can upgrade flink-runner version to flink-1.8.2 as soon as possible, at least we can merge this in Beam 2.17 release.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;What do you think?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16919379" author="mxm" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2019 09:51:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=sunjincheng121&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;sunjincheng121&quot;&gt;sunjincheng121&lt;/a&gt;! It would be great to propose a 1.8.2 release, as the above has been a blocker for users on Flink 1.8.1. The work on the Beam side is very minimal (i.e. just change the version identifier). If necessary, we probably have a few more days after the release cut on Sep 11 for critical patches like this one.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That said, it would be great to start a discussion for 1.8.2 as soon as possible. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16919398" author="sunjincheng121" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2019 10:22:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mxm&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mxm&quot;&gt;mxm&lt;/a&gt; for your confirmation, I have already initiated the discussion of the flink release 1.8.2. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16919423" author="sunjincheng121" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2019 10:56:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I would like to fix this issue after flink-1.8.2 released.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16919858" author="mxm" created="Fri, 30 Aug 2019 20:02:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16926290" author="sunjincheng121" created="Tue, 10 Sep 2019 03:07:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mxm&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mxm&quot;&gt;mxm&lt;/a&gt;&#160;Beam 2.16 release branch will be cut in 3 days, So It&apos;s great if you have time to look at the VOTE of flink-1.8.2 release. &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16929227" author="sunjincheng121" created="Fri, 13 Sep 2019 14:16:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;1.8.2 Already released.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16930911" author="mxm" created="Mon, 16 Sep 2019 22:24:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged to master. Backporting to the 2.16.0 branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
